( Carnage: I do believe that I know that Prowl is at the Cybertronien Fire, Yanshosh. If you care to read again, so does Dinobot.

-Prowl was a flyer and, thus, would reach the Alliance base before him if they were to leave the Maximals ship at the same time, then being forced to wait for his arrival. A process that was not acceptable, ever second counted.
So of Dinobot was to break off from his course and diverted towards the Alliance base he should arrive just as Prowl did, thus no time was wasted at all.
The distance was great and his land for could not go as fast as a flyer, they simply flew over the trees and forests he had to pick his way through.
With his mind then decided Dinobot then broke off from his dead run and arche towards the Alliance base as an even faster pace, not having any time to explain in the hope that Prowl would simply understand.-

As you may be able to tell, Dinobot is simply on his way towards the Alliance base so that he would be there when Prowl GOT THERE and not waste time for the owl-Maximals to wait for him.
Simple enough answer to straighten things out.
Any ferther questions, Yanshosh, please feel free to mail me. I shall be pleased to give reliefe to any furture concerns.)
